pull.title: RPC: why not give more details when "generate" fails?
pull.body: It should be unlikely to get this error anyway, but when you get it, the more you know about it better, no?

events.body: Commit message is a bit cheeky for my tastes, but content utACK. It's better to give something to user than nothing.
